  <span id="freeText16885125253021807438" style="display:none">Received a complimentary copy of the book to read and review.I must admit first and foremost that I don’t usually read historical romance but this one was an exception. When I read the blurb for it I knew I had to. I couldn’t put it down once I started reading it. It’s a real page turner. It has some great twists and turns. It will appeal to all readers who love a good book. I love the world and the characters that Kim created with this one. The plot is great. I highly recommend it be added to your TBR list. I look forward to reading more of Kim’s books.<br /></span>
